snippet.title: 'Nonsense' or necessary? HOA board approves $82,000 in assessments to challenge trademark of name
snippet.description: Stonebriar Improvement Association, Inc. residents are assessed $2,000 to pay legal fees for a lawsuit over a small plastic shed and to mount a challenge to the homeowner's trademark claim.
